  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient older than 18 years.

          -  Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Associated lesser metatarsals surgery.

          -  Associated surgery on midfoot, hindfoot or ankle.

          -  Neurologic diseases (Charcot Marie Tooth disease, polyomyelitis, compartment syndrome
             sequelae)

          -  Clinical or X-ray degenerative signs (Hallux rigidus) or irreducible deformations
             (MTP1 arthrodesis indications).

          -  Patient who declined the study.
      </textblock>
